------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Geant4 application for simulation of interaction of a charged particle with copper block.
Feb 2025
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Main program       : main.cc
Primary particle   : proton (and charged pion) *
World material     : Galactic (vacuum)
Material           : copper (20mmx20mmx5mm)
Output root files  : output0.root, output1.root

Aim of the program is to fill root ntuples containing the following
data associated to proton (and pion) after interaction with Cu block:

container name: Hits
- Event number (0,1,2,...)
- Particle's PDG code (p=2212, pi=211, ...)
- Particle's momentum magnitude (MeV)
- Particle's x,y,z components of momentum (MeV)
- Particle's x,y,z values on sensitve detector (mm)

container name: Scoring
- Energy deposition in MeV of particle in Cu

Compile and run in build folder

$ cmake ..
$ make
$ ./main
or 
$ ./main z-run.mac
____________________________
* Particle candidates are: 
GenericIon He3 alpha anti_He3 anti_alpha anti_deuteron anti_doublehyperH4 anti_doublehyperdoubleneutron anti_hyperH4 
anti_hyperHe5 anti_hyperalpha anti_hypertriton anti_lambda anti_neutron anti_nu_e anti_nu_mu 
anti_proton anti_triton chargedgeantino deuteron doublehyperH4 doublehyperdoubleneutron e+ e- gamma 
geantino hyperH4 hyperHe5 hyperalpha hypertriton kaon+ kaon- lambda mu+ mu- neutron nu_e nu_mu pi+ pi- 
pi0 proton triton ion
